yekka-d seg uẓar (BR) yemmal-d anamek n wayen yettɣiman aṭas mebla ma yeswa aman,  am ulɣem  (Taïfi  sb.25).  Sawalen-as i uslem-agi aburi, acku yezga d awḥid, imi yettêizi iman-is ɣef tewtemt-is. Neqqar daɣen awal-agi Aburi (neɣ ibur) i wergaz ur nezwiǧ ara. Yettwileɣ s tagetnamka, acku yiwen wawal yesɛa aîas inumak, yezmer ad yili d aslem, d abaɛli, neɣ d amdan ur nezwiğ ara. Aburi d aslem buyiɣes. Yesɛa iɣil deg teɣzi  (50  isuntimen), ma di taẓeyt yesɛa sin n  kilu.Tulmisin ines d tigi : aqerruy-is yemsel sufella,  icenfiren-is d izuranen, ɣur-s sin yeɛruren ; amezwaru yesɛa  isennanen, yesɛa daɣen  tiqcert d timdewert d tameqqrant.
